title: [Frostmain Docks, Starboard Pier]
[Frostmain, Starboard Pier]
description: The easternmost of the trio of piers is a mess of creaky planks spotted heavily with the droppings of seafowl.  Waters to either side are deep, black, and cold.  Stinging salt is so thick on the air as to have left cakes of gleaming grit on the nearby pylons.
